<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr" lang="en">

    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <!-- Tell the browser to be responsive to screen width -->
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <title>Home | Crime Tracker</title>
        <!-- Favicon icon -->
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/images/police-handcuffs.png" >
        <!-- Custom CSS -->
        <link href="plugins/bower_components/chartist/dist/chartist.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="plugins/bower_components/chartist-plugin-tooltips/dist/chartist-plugin-tooltip.css">
        <!-- Custom CSS -->
        <link href="css/style.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    </head>

    <body>
    <div id="main-wrapper" data-layout="vertical" data-navbarbg="skin5" data-sidebartype="full"
        data-sidebar-position="absolute" data-header-position="absolute" data-boxed-layout="full">
        <!-- Topbar header - style you can find in pages.scss -->
        <header class="topbar" data-navbarbg="skin5">
            <nav class="navbar top-navbar navbar-expand-md navbar-dark">
                <div class="navbar-header" data-logobg="skin6">
                    <!-- Logo -->
                    <a class="navbar-brand" href="/home">
                        <b class="logo-icon">
                            <!-- Dark Logo icon -->
                            <img src="images/police-handcuffs.png" alt="homepage" width="50" height="50"/>
                        </b>
                        <span class="logo-text">
                            <!-- dark Logo text -->
                            <img src="images/images.jpg" alt="homepage" />
                        </span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </header>
        </div>
        <div id="main-wrapper" data-layout="vertical" data-navbarbg="skin5" data-sidebartype="full" data-sidebar-position="absolute" data-header-position="absolute" data-boxed-layout="full">
          <%- include('partials/header') %>
          <div class="page-wrapper">
        
             <!-- Bread crumb and right sidebar toggle -->
        
            <div class="page-breadcrumb bg-white">
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12">
                        <h4 style="font-size :35px;"class="page-title">Welcome To Crime Tracker</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- /.col-lg-12 -->
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 style="font-size: 25px;">Hello There! <br></h2>
                <p style="font-size: 25px;">This is a crime tracker system,which lets the user view the report activities that may have occured within their location, view trends and frequent patterns of crime
                </p>
            </div>
        
            <div class="container-fluid">
                <!-- 6 Categories -->
                <div class="row justify-content-center">

                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
                        <div class="white-box ">
                            <h3 style="font-size :30px;"class="box-title">Report Crime</h3>
                            <div>
                              <p style="font-size :25px;">This is the feature that allows a user to report crime activities that occured by filling in crime report form. Can enquire and attach more documentaional evidence.
                                Which will help South African police with the investigation of the crime.
                            </p>
                                <a href="/report-crime" class="btn btn-primary">Report Crime</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
                        <div class="white-box ">
                            <h3 style="font-size :30px;" class="box-title">Crime Hotspot - View Map</h3>
                            <p style="font-size :25px;">This is where a user will view their preferred hotspot crime areas and will be graphically represented using a real life geographic map. <br><br><br>
                            </p>
                            <div>
                                <a href="/view-crimes" class="btn btn-primary">Crime Hotspots</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12">
                        <div class="white-box ">
                            <h3 style="font-size :30px;"class="box-title">View Crime Statistics</h3>
                            <p style="font-size :25px;">This is where a user is able to view crimes reported their preferred hotspot crime areas and will be graphically represented using a real life geographic map. <br><br><br>
                            </p>
                            <div>
                                <a href="/view-statistics" class="btn btn-primary">Statistics</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
          <%- include('partials/footer') %> 
    </body>
</html>
